{"tid":1395492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請唔好再捐錢畀物資隊","createTime":"2019-08-01T18:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T03:13:35.000Z","uid":110646,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f8a58dcf203a45e4dc478295a2282387200fdc29","tid":1395492,"uid":110646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:29:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出黎發夢請直接捐物資畀前線！</span></span><br />\n首先好多謝物資隊幫手買物資 <br />\n你哋唔單止出錢出力 仲要承受俾人沒收物資甚至俾人拉嘅風險同壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要裝備 要裝備 要裝備</span></span><br />\n裝備係前線最缺 亦都較易比狗沒收<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以最低風險係</span></span>我哋幫自己全屋企人買一套裝備<br />\n（個人保護用途）<br />\n再係發夢時帶多一套畀前線<br />\n一到發夢現場就傳去前面<br />\n最好長期有人幫手企係後面唔同位置叫人捐/傳物資去前面<br />\n中間後面人數多過前線好多倍<br />\n所以每人帶多一套已經幫到好多！！！<br />\n就算中途俾狗截 得一套都易啲搵藉口解圍<br />\n<br />\n一個人或者一team幾個人購買幾十/幾百套裝備<br />\n如果物資被沒收/手足被捕 大家心裡會十分難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以希望大家唔好只捐錢 要出埋一分力！</span></span><br />\n五金舖/運動用品店賣嘅裝係佢哋日常銷售嘅產品<br />\n可以合理出售 我哋個人用途都可以合理購買<br />\n需求大左 啲舖入多啲貨都好合理<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋一齊出一分力好不好？</span></span>"},{"pid":"15639e933d1f59b25111ec417fafa3b238e39554","tid":1395492,"uid":110646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:33:45.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"88495e6764b5d9c69497b5e4a41a208081f754c3","tid":1395492,"uid":110646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:42:15.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"0b82ab2508037b739ff7085b8d941ce4a77840c0","tid":1395492,"uid":110646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:42:17.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2b00f738ac0d88d26e292f471009a8761126004b","tid":1395492,"uid":110646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:48:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23f7934ffa2414a0e3ebdff2c218ed6d97ba27df","tid":1395492,"uid":110646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:12:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40c9f6a701ba847b8e8d4689ffa1ce27a9999c23","tid":1395492,"uid":269428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35428af428b7ff54fb1600d2bb58d414fee3152d","tid":1395492,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8682806158afff5d4c71a1a50d731d23854f830e","tid":1395492,"uid":110646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}